        <abstract> 
<p>Has read FMM’s article in <hi rend="italic">Contemporary Review</hi> [25 (1875): 305–26].</p>  
<p>Never suspected FMM was responsible for the <hi rend="italic">Quarterly Review</hi> article ["Primitive man", <hi rend="italic">Q. Rev.</hi> 137 (1874): 40–77]; knows it was written by Mivart.</p> 
        </abstract>
